      "value": "<p><strong>Level 3</strong> Evocation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> line</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a bit of fur and a crystal rod)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nA stroke of lightning forming a 100-foot-long, 5-foot-wide Line [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Line blasts out from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the Line [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Line makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 8d6 Lightning damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 8d6|3-9|1d6 for each spell slot level above 3.</p>",
